find out we killed him?

16
00:00:53.121 --> 00:00:55.323
I want to go back.
It's not safe there.

17
00:00:55.456 --> 00:00:57.191
I do believe I felt
some trepidation

18
00:00:57.325 --> 00:00:59.493
