69
00:03:59.773 --> 00:04:01.573
[Raglan in Japanese]
Gochisousama. Taisho-san.

70
00:04:01.642 --> 00:04:03.110
[Raglan coughs]

71
00:04:04.545 --> 00:04:07.615
[â™ª light classical
music continues]

72
00:04:23.331 --> 00:04:25.966
